  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK469">
<l>naṉṟāṟṟa luḷḷun tavaṟuṇ ṭavaravar</l>
<l>paṇpaṟin tāṟṟāk kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are failures even in acting well, when it is done without knowing the various dispositions of men.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
